This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image compression. It may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it involves processing and compressing multimedia data. The paper proposes a recurrent neural network approach, which suggests it may belong to the information theory (cs.IT) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques, which could place it in the machine learning (cs.LG) or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
